"```sql\nSELECT AVG(hero_attribute.attribute_value) AS average_attribute_value\nFROM hero_attribute\nJOIN superhero ON hero_attribute.hero_id = superhero.id\nWHERE superhero.alignment_id = 3;\n```\n\nThis SQL query calculates the average attribute value of all neutral superheroes by joining the `hero_attribute` and `superhero` tables and filtering for superheroes with an `alignment_id` of 3, which corresponds to neutral alignment."